{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "燕七看到郭大路跟活剥皮拿银子走了，认定他做了走狗，气得眼泪直流。林太平和王动分析活剥皮的用意——五百两银子必有所图，多半是见不得人的事。王动点出燕七之所以如此生气，是因为对郭大路用情太深，才会往最坏处想。郭大路回来后，燕七冷言冷语称他为走狗，郭大路伤心离去。王动从郭大路身上搜出当票——他当掉了金链子和金鸡心换银子买食物，真相大白。燕七愧疚不已，郭大路主动拿出酒来讲和，两人和好如初。燕七流着泪笑，郭大路说王动最了解他，林太平最同情他，而燕七对他最凶却也最好。郭大路表示要去找活剥皮算计，燕七同行，两人在雪地里互相表白情谊。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "因为我亲眼看到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "看到什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "看到他跟活剥皮哐咕了半天，活剥皮拿出了锭银子给他，他就跟活剥皮走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你没有追过去问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我追去干什么？我又不想做活剥皮的跟班。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如只不过是做跟班，跟着他到城里去走一趟，倒也没什么关系，但我看这件事绝不会如此简单。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "活剥皮自己也说过，他这样做必定另有用意，我看他绝不会干什么好事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "能让活剥皮这种人心甘情愿拿出五百两银子来的，只有一种事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "哪种事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "赚五千两银子的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不错，若非一本万利的事，他绝不肯掏腰包拿出五百两银子来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "真正能一本万利，也只有一种事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "见不得人的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我看他不是去偷，就是去骗，又生怕别人发觉后对他不客气，所以才来找我们做他的保镖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "连你都能想得到，他怎么会想不到，他又不比别人笨。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你若认为他不该去，为什么不拦着他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "一个人若是自己往泥坑跳，别人就算想拉，也拉不住的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "所以你就眼看着他跳下去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你在说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "我在说，到现在我还是不信小郭会做这种事，你呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我……我也不太相信。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "你至少总还有点怀疑，是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "但燕七却一点也不怀疑，已认定了小郭会做那种事，你可知道为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我也有点奇怪，他和小郭的交情本来好像特别好。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "就因为交情特别好，所以才相信些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么呢？我不懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "朱珠忽然失踪，我们都想到可能有别的原因，但小郭却想不到，所以就往最坏的地方去想，那又是为了什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "因为他对朱珠用情太深，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "所以脑筋就不清楚了，对不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "你老对一个人用情很深，那么你对他的判断就不会正确；因为，你平时只能看到他的好处，但只要一有了个小小的变化和打击，你就立刻会自责自怨，患得患失，所以就忍不住往最坏的地方去想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你的意思我懂，只不过这比喻却好像不太恰当。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你怎么能拿朱珠和小郭的事来比？小郭对朱珠的情感，怎会跟燕七对小郭的情感一样？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "你想出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "今天天气好了些，我想出去打扞。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也去，今天再不出去打扞，只怕就真的要饿死了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "小郭身上既然有了银子，就绝不会让我们饿死，你为什么不等他回来？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我为什么要等他回来？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "就算为了我，行不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "他若不回来呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "他若不回来，我就请你们吃狗肉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这种天气，到哪里找狗去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "用不着找，这里就有一条。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "狗在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你是狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "不但是狗，而且是条土狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "一个人若连自己的朋友是哪种人都分不出，不是土狗是什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小郭身上既然有了银子，就绝不会让我们饿死，你为什么不等他回来？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你——假如你开家饭馆子，生意一定不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这倒是好主意，只可惜还有一样不对……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "哪样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我那饭铺生意再好，开不了三天也得关门。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "就算我自己没有把自己吃垮，你们也会来把我吃垮的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "放心，我绝不会去吃你的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你在生气，我又有什么地方得罪了你？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你自己心里明白。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我明白什么？——我一点也不明白。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你虽然不是土狗，但这里却有条走狗！土狗还没关系，走狗我却受不了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "谁是走狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你以为我做了活剥皮的走狗？你以为这些东西是我用他给我的定金买来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "这些东西难道是天上掉下来的、地上长出来的不成？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "好，好……你说我是走狗，我就是走狗……你受不了我，我走。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你先看看这是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是当票。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你再看清楚些，当的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "当票是我刚才从小郭身上摸出来的，我早就告诉过你们，我若是改行做小偷，现在早就发财了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我现在懒得动。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你……你不生气了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "本来是很生气的，但后来想了想，非但不生气反而开心。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "开心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你若不关心我，我就算做了乌龟王八蛋，和你一点关系都没有，你也用不着生气的。就因为你是我的好朋友，才会对我发脾气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "可是……我本不该冤枉你的，我本来应该信得过你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你冤枉我也没关系，揍我两拳也没关系，只要是我的好朋友，随便干什么都没关系。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "肯不肯讲和？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我在想，酸梅汤的光眼真不错，你若肯洗洗脸，一定是个很漂亮的小伙子，也许比我还漂亮得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你死盯着我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "谁做你的老婆，那才是倒了八辈子穷霉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来不喜欢喝酒，但今天却真想喝个大醉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "只可惜今天我不能陪你醉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "因为，今天我还有事，还得下山去一趟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "下山去干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我跟一个人有约会。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "跟谁有约会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "活剥皮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你跟他约好了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "他没有约我，我却要去找他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "找他干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "他肯出五百两银子，一定没存什么好主意，所以我要去看看，他究竟想要剥谁的皮？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "今天，我又发现了一件事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我发现王老大实在了解我，天下只怕再也找不出第二个人能这么了解我的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他的确最能了解别人，不但是你，所有的人他都了解。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "但最同情我的人却是林太平，我看得出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你既不了解我，也不同情我；你不但对我最凶，而且好像随时随地都在跟我斗嘴，员气……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "但也不知为什么，我还是觉得对我最好的也是你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "有时我对你简直气得要命，譬如说今天，王老大若那样对我，我也许反而不会那么样生气，也许立刻就会对他解释，可是你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你只对我生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "那也只因为我对你特别好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "究竟有多好，连我也说不出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "说不出来就是假的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "但我却可以打个比喻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "为了王老大，我会将所有的衣服都当光，只穿着条底裤回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "但为了你，我可以将这条底裤都拿去当了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "谁要你那条破底裤。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我虽已发誓不成亲，但你若是女的，我一定要娶你做老婆。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    }
